'''The Tolkien Calendar 1994''' is a Polish calendar published by Seckja Tolkienowska, Poland ([[Polish Tolkien Society]]). The calendar features pen and ink illustrations by [[Helena Strokowska]], [[Ryszard Derdziński]], [[Maciej]], [[Wygnanski]], [[Karolina Stopa]], and [[Małgorzata Pudlik]].

* Dimensions: 8 1/4 x 11 1/2 inches
* Clear plastic cover (front and back)
* Red comb bound
